com.intel.jndn.utils.repository

Class ForLoopRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.jndn.utils.repository.ForLoopRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Repository

    public class ForLoopRepository
extends Object
implements Repository
    Store Data packets in a linked list and iterate over the list to find the best match; this is a subset of the functionality provided in MemoryContentCache and borrows the matching logic from there. Code for removing stale packets is not yet implemented.
    Author:
    Andrew Brown
